      "title_zh": "Bugcrowd 发布 Savant AI 战略引发争议：利用白帽黑客报告训练 AI 代理进行自动化测试",
      "title_orig": "RT shubs: https://www.bugcrowd.com/blog/savant-bugcrowds-ai-strategy-for-preemptive-security/ so the bug bounty community freaked out a few weeks ago ...",
